1.title: New Beginnings, Old Tensions

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

1.plot: As Jentina and Roisin embark on their search for the 'Gypsy and Traveller Face of the Year', simmering tensions from their previous working relationship erupt and the contest gets off to the worse possible start

2.title: Off and Running?

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

2.plot: The contestants begin to sign up but Jentina doubts Roisin's gypsy credentials and the girls head out on their own in search of talent.

3.title: Welcome to Stow

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

3.plot: Episode 3- The girls search the festival.

4.title: Race to the Heat

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

4.plot: The first heat in the competition takes place at Epsom Races, but Roisin and Jentina aren't talking to each other and the contestants are out of control!

5.title: Luck of the Irish!

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

5.plot: The girls head to Ireland on the next leg of their search. After an appearance on Irish TV they sign up two very unusual contestants but there are concerns about the upcoming final.

6.title: Are You Going to Appleby Fair?

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

6.plot: Appleby Fair, the biggest event in the gypsy calendar is next for the girls where they hold their second heat. A contestant reveals his love for Jentina and a gypsy legend agrees to enter the competition.

7.title: Boot Camp

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

7.plot: The contestants head to London for some media training ahead of what they might expect to face if they win the contest. But not everyone can handle the heat. Tension erupts as contestants begin to crack under the pressure

8.title: The Final

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

8.plot: Eight contestants step onto the stage at the grand London final. Nerves are shredded as some rise and some fall... spectacularly! Who will be crowned 'Gypsy and Traveller Face of the Year' and will Jentina and Roisin ever get back on speaking terms!

1.title: The Big Audition

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

1.plot: Still searching for a stage on which to audition, Harley the performing pony gets his first taste of the TV big time as Gypsy Journalist Jake Bowers promotes his talent show for Travellers on ITV's This Morning.

2.title: Southbank Centre

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

2.plot: This week, travelers invade the prestigious home of arts and entertainment, London's Southbank Centre. The centre's hosted hundreds of cultural events but never a Gypsy knees up and our cameras capture the chaos at this third heat of the hotly fought competition.

3.title: The Heat

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

3.plot: Jake is hauled to his sponsor's for an ear bashing. He's forced to admit that there's a problem with numbers at the upcoming heat in the North West.

4.title: The Great Celebration

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

4.plot: Hundreds of travelers and gypsies have gathered in a field in Essex to celebrate God. Journalist Jake Bowers is covering the Light and Life Christian Convention for The Travellers' Time.

5.title: At The Fair

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

5.plot: Romany Gypsy Violet Cannon, an activist and author, visits the Lee Gap Horse Fair in Yorkshire. Violet introduces us to her Dad, who's been selling horses here for years.

6.title: Dale Farm

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

6.plot: Dale Farm in Essex, Britain's most controversial Travellers site, has run out of time. The resident's notice of eviction has run out, and the bailiffs are moving in.

7.title: The Grand Finale

episode of.title: A Gypsy Life for Me (TV Series 2010– )

7.plot: D Day, the Grand Finale of the Gypsy talent show, has arrived - but there's trouble at the top. Jake and Tracy have fallen out. Tracy wants a spot on the stage and her share of the limelight but Jake doesn't think she's up to it. Will everything come together in time for the finale?
